      li.fragment 1996: Standard vom W3C <a href="http://www.w3.org/History.html" target="_blank">W3C History</a>
      li.fragment 2004: WHATWG-Gründung <a href="https://whatwg.org/news/start" target="_blank">Mailing-Liste</a>
